{"tid":1367342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人發起募捐安全帽 支援香港人示威 反應熱列","createTime":"2019-07-26T08:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:38:43.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1ed6ab3256bd16f3c23bec2ea479938978b318","tid":1367342,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"［0725台北西門募集二手安全帽撐香港］<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本次約募集兩百餘頂安全帽⛑️，感謝大家的幫忙！<br />\n<br />\n因為發起時程較緊急，無法讓全台各地的民眾一起即時加入，若有新的募集行動，我們會再協助分享行動資訊給大家，請大家幫我們分享出去。<br />\n<br />\n目前也收到訊息表示淘寶禁止安全帽販售至香港，我們深感遺憾也強烈譴責不尊重人權的政府！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aidwc6E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faidwc6E.png&h=4a5cd88a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2a83e8a8c40ed13657a6f234bb8640679b44208","tid":1367342,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}